         <p>
            
            Meta/Z is a project build by a software engineering team from OTO. 
      
            
            <br/>
            
            We are developing software that will act as an aggregating web 
      front-end to retrieve information from several content databases that contain various metadata value
      assigned didactic products (so called learnobjects). 
            
            <br/>
            
            The web application 
      offers its users an efficient way of searching and accessing the content 
      by full text and metadata search.
         
